{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/blog/2015-01-17-juzhen-fangsong/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"少年读书隙中窥月"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"6e8b2213-5027-5490-b02f-22458b7e6a86","excerpt":"由开发了康熙字典体的厉向晨同学发布的文悦古体仿宋发布了，面向非商业应用免费，对于我来说是一个好消息，在此深表谢意。 之前就决定日志 LOGO 要用宋体或者楷体，但是好用的宋体实在是不好找，普通的例如博雅宋之类的太文字化，没有图形区分度，别的好看的宋体都是要大把大把钱的，例如 TP…","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2c5523cc06f6acb83d6c0532c8e2d03d/07a9c/juzhenfangsong.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"juzhenfangsong\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/2c5523cc06f6acb83d6c0532c8e2d03d/fcda8/juzhenfangsong.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2c5523cc06f6acb83d6c0532c8e2d03d/12f09/juzhenfangsong.png 148w,\n/static/2c5523cc06f6acb83d6c0532c8e2d03d/e4a3f/juzhenfangsong.png 295w,\n/static/2c5523cc06f6acb83d6c0532c8e2d03d/fcda8/juzhenfangsong.png 590w,\n/static/2c5523cc06f6acb83d6c0532c8e2d03d/efc66/juzhenfangsong.png 885w,\n/static/2c5523cc06f6acb83d6c0532c8e2d03d/c83ae/juzhenfangsong.png 1180w,\n/static/2c5523cc06f6acb83d6c0532c8e2d03d/07a9c/juzhenfangsong.png 1440w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>由开发了康熙字典体的<a href=\"http://www.zhihu.com/people/Digidea\">厉向晨</a>同学发布的文悦古体仿宋发布了，面向非商业应用免费，对于我来说是一个好消息，在此深表谢意。</p>\n<p>之前就决定日志 LOGO 要用宋体或者楷体，但是好用的宋体实在是不好找，普通的例如博雅宋之类的太文字化，没有图形区分度，别的好看的宋体都是要大把大把钱的，例如 <a href=\"http://www.typeproject.com/font/tpmincho/\">TP 明朝</a>，如果我买得起的话，肯定会大用特用。现在的日志 LOGO 所用的字体是方正清刻本悦宋，个人授权。这字体古意是足够了， 美中不足在于只有简体……</p>\n<p>看到这个字体发布，感觉又有想法来写代码了，我决定还是坚持当初的阅读中心以及简单化风格，首要就是把侧边栏砍掉，至于什么时候开工……看心情。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"聚珍仿宋","publish_date":"2015-01-17T03:05:17.000+08:00","revise_date":"2015-01-17T03:05:17.000+08:00","draft":false}}},"pageContext":{"previous":{"id":"146d9e06-401a-5fe4-bc2a-220242b1e1c2","fields":{"slug":"/blog/2015-01-14-20150104/","type":"blog","timeToRead":{"words":969,"minutes":6}},"frontmatter":{"title":"2015 年 1 月 14 日","publish_date":"2015-01-14T01:18:51.000+08:00"}},"slug":"/blog/2015-01-17-juzhen-fangsong/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1330398833","2356112386"],"slicesMap":{}}